---
import EventLayout from "../../components/EventLayout.astro";

const images = [
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-iii/1.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon III" },
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-iii/4.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon III" },
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-iii/9.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon III" },
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-iii/5.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon III" },
  { src: "/ai-hackathon-iii/7.jpg", alt: "AI Hackathon III" },
];
---

<EventLayout
  title="AI Hackathon III"
  date="August 30, 2025"
  location="The Beacon, Antwerp"
  type="Hackathon"
  description="Change The Outcome - over 400 man-hours of innovation packed into one weekend at The Beacon."
  images={images}
>
  <p>The third edition was the most intense yet. People with conviction came together on a Saturday, during summer, and built something meaningful. That's what changes the outcome.</p>
  <p>Winners spanned an LLM search optimization tool using browser automation, Echo Journal - a globally connected AI journaling app, and belgiumtechchat - a scraper for major event websites. The energy, creativity, and technical skill on display made this weekend unforgettable.</p>
  <p>Thank you to <strong>The Beacon</strong> for hosting, to our judges for their time, and to every hacker, mentor, and supporter who made it happen.</p>
</EventLayout>
